data.description: Nestled in the heart of Lenoir City, this newly renovated ranch-style home seamlessly combines modern comforts with timeless charm. With three bedrooms and two full baths this home is both stylish and functional. The open floor plan creates a warm and inviting atmosphere, perfect for both everyday living and entertaining guests. The well-appointed kitchen, with sleek countertops and state-of-the-art appliances, is the heart of the home, leading to a screened-in patio where indoor and outdoor living blend effortlessly. Beyond lies a private oasis--a deck overlooking a shimmering pool, and fire pit to gather around and create evening memories, surrounded by a fenced yard destined for memorable moments. An additional lot, gives this property almost an acre and provides endless possibilities for landscaping or expansion. Don't miss the chance to make this house your home. Closing on the house must be Jan 31, 2024.
